Copies of the originals are fetched from the Goose repository and
can be retrieved via:

  gh api repos/aaif-goose/goose/contents/documentation/src/pages/recipes/data/recipes/<recipe>.yaml

The adaptations in this repository are derivative works that translate
the recipes from Goose's YAML/Jinja2 workflow format into Claude Code
slash commands. Structural changes include:

  - Replacement of Goose 'subrecipes' with Claude Code subagent calls
  - Replacement of Jinja2 templating with slash-command $ARGUMENTS
  - Integration with Claude HQ Commander protocol references
  - Removal of Goose-specific extension configuration blocks

